caption.title: Graph of the qPCR results.
caption.p: Presenting the leptin (p<0.05), IL-6 (p<0.01), IFN-γ (p<0.05) and IGF-1 (p<0.05) mRNA levels; “*” at the top of the bars indicates which analysis revealed a significant difference compared with the control. All data are expressed as the number of fold-changes.
